       fhir:v "Laboratory system that polls the Lab Order Repository for orders directed to it (FHIR search on Task by recipient and status — transaction ② — order pull), claims them by updating Task status, and performs the requested testing. In the Zimbabwe national architecture this role is played by the Senaite LIMS."
